      <description>Let me regale you with a story of bulkhead number 2.
(This may be more interesting to people who are actually building Beg Meil. In fact, I write this mostly in hopes that it makes it easier for future builders.)
A few things that are helpful to know:
Each of the bulkheads is numbers, with station 1 being near the transom (stern), and station 8 near the stem (front). So, the bulkhead in question is near the back of the boat.</description>
