      <guid>https://boat.karlnelson.net/posts/12-sixteen-sides/</guid>
      <description>Take the gaff from eight sides to sixteen was one of the easier steps in the process, mostly because there just isn&amp;rsquo;t that much wood to remove. And because there isn&amp;rsquo;t much wood, the plane takes off these lovely ten-foot-long shavings of wood.
The end result is something that approximates round.
