    <item>
      <title>Which Boat?</title>
      <link>https://boat.karlnelson.net/posts/2-which-boat/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jan 2022 09:00:00 -0700</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://boat.karlnelson.net/posts/2-which-boat/</guid>
      <description>I decided I wanted to build a boat.
Among other questions, it does raise the issue of which boat?
A few years ago, I took some sailing lessons, and been sailing occasionally ever since. So, it&amp;rsquo;d be a sailboat. (If I were to get a powerboat, sign me up for something in the style of a Lake Union Dreamboat.)
The boats I learned to sail on are Blanchard Junior Knockabouts at Seattle&amp;rsquo;s Center for Wooden Boats.</description>
