    <item>
      <title>Why?</title>
      <link>https://boat.karlnelson.net/posts/1-why/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 01 Jan 2022 09:00:00 -0700</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://boat.karlnelson.net/posts/1-why/</guid>
      <description>Deciding to build a boat is a sign you&amp;rsquo;re planting your feet firmly in the &amp;ldquo;journey&amp;rdquo; camp, not the &amp;ldquo;destination&amp;rdquo; camp. Which is to say, if you&amp;rsquo;re interested in going boating, there are plenty of easier and faster ways to get on the water. But, I&amp;rsquo;m up for the journey, and under no illusions about how long this particular journey might take.
None of that really answers the question of why I want to build a boat.</description>
